Git diff compares staging area and working directory
git diff -- staged compares previous commit with new staged area 
Notes of git 
git log --stat = give very short summary of all commit
git log --pretty=oneline = give commit information in one line
git log --pretty=short = give commit information in short
git log --pretty=full = same as short but also give author and commitor name
git log --since=2.weeks = give all changes in file since 2 weeks
git log --since=2.days = same as above but since 2 days
git log --since=2.months =  same as above but since 2 months
git log --pretty=format:"%h -- %an" = /an = author name/, /h = commit hash/

